Package com.threerings.nexus.distrib

Interface Summary
DAttribute The base type for all Nexus object attributes.
DService.Factory<T extends NexusService> Used to create service attributes.
EventSink Handles the dispatch of events for a NexusObject.
Keyed An interface that must be implemented by keyed entities.
NexusService A marker interface identifying a Nexus distributed service.
NexusService.ObjectResponse If the object returned in a Callback contains any NexusObjects, the returned object must implement this interface and provide a reference to the contained objects.
Singleton A marker interface for Nexus singleton entities.
 

Class Summary
Address<T extends NexusObject> Identifies a distributed object somewhere in the Nexus network.
Address.OfAnonymous An address of an anonymous object.
Address.OfKeyed<T extends NexusObject & Keyed> An address of a keyed object.
Address.OfSingleton<T extends NexusObject & Singleton> An address of a singleton object.
DAttribute.Event A base class for all events associated with an attribute.
DistribUtil Provides access to interfaces that should not be called by normal clients, but which must be accessible to the Nexus implementation code, which may reside in a different package.
DMap<K,V> A map attribute for a Nexus object.
DService<T extends NexusService> An attribute that contains a Nexus service reference.
DService.Dispatcher<T extends NexusService> An implementation detail used by service dispatchers.
DSet<T> A set attribute for a Nexus object.
DSignal<T> A signal attribute which retains no data, but serves as a means by which to emit and listen for custom events.
DValue<T> A value attribute for a Nexus object.
NexusEvent Contains information describing a change to a NexusObject.
NexusObject The basis for all distributed information sharing in Nexus.
Streamer_Address<T extends NexusObject> Handles the streaming of Address and/or nested classes.
Streamer_Address.OfAnonymous Handles the streaming of Address.OfAnonymous instances.
Streamer_Address.OfKeyed<T extends NexusObject & Keyed> Handles the streaming of Address.OfKeyed instances.
Streamer_Address.OfSingleton<T extends NexusObject & Singleton> Handles the streaming of Address.OfSingleton instances.
Streamer_Address.OfTyped<T extends NexusObject> Handles the streaming of Streamer_Address.OfTyped instances.
Streamer_DAttribute Handles the streaming of DAttribute and/or nested classes.
Streamer_DAttribute.Event Handles the streaming of DAttribute.Event instances.
Streamer_DMap Handles the streaming of DMap and/or nested classes.
Streamer_DMap.PutEvent<K,V> Handles the streaming of Streamer_DMap.PutEvent instances.
Streamer_DMap.RemoveEvent<K,V> Handles the streaming of Streamer_DMap.RemoveEvent instances.
Streamer_DSet Handles the streaming of DSet and/or nested classes.
Streamer_DSet.AddEvent<T> Handles the streaming of Streamer_DSet.AddEvent instances.
Streamer_DSet.RemoveEvent<T> Handles the streaming of Streamer_DSet.RemoveEvent instances.
Streamer_DSignal Handles the streaming of DSignal and/or nested classes.
Streamer_DSignal.EmitEvent<T> Handles the streaming of Streamer_DSignal.EmitEvent instances.
Streamer_DValue Handles the streaming of DValue and/or nested classes.
Streamer_DValue.ChangeEvent<T> Handles the streaming of Streamer_DValue.ChangeEvent instances.
Streamer_NexusEvent Handles the streaming of NexusEvent and/or nested classes.
 

Exception Summary
NexusException An exception used to report failure of Nexus services.
